<br>
30 seconds to cast rune 4 and still consumes a peridot.  That cast time is so long i could probably regen that much mana in less time, the consumption of a peridot is very expensive for a click effect.  Then theres the final end question of rune 4?  At the level required to get this item rune 4 is trivial.  Unless there is a level 51 or lower chanter out there who can state that they have a robe from hot already, and im not talking about MQing.<br>
